name: Texas football
summary: In a highly anticipated matchup, No. 1 Texas dominated No. 18 Oklahoma in the Red River Rivalry with a convincing 34-3 victory. The win had a symbolic twist as Texas players planted their flag through a Baker Mayfield Oklahoma jersey. Details regarding the upcoming Georgia-Texas football game on October 19th were also announced. Texas' defense has been impressive, allowing an average of just 7 points per game. In high school football, Texas' rankings for Week 6 were released by Dave Campbell's Texas Football. CBS Sports provided live stream information for the Texas vs. Oklahoma game, along with odds and predictions. The victory over Oklahoma was celebrated with a symbolic gesture known as "Light the Tower" by Texas Football.

name: Purdue vs Illinois
summary: On Saturday, October 12th, Purdue Boilermakers faced the #23 ranked Illinois Fighting Illini in the 100th edition of their rivalry game for the Cannon Trophy. Ahead of the game, experts and media outlets released their predictions, odds, and game previews. Despite Illinois being favored, the game went into overtime and ended in a thrilling 50-49 victory for Illinois. The game was highlighted by the performances of both quarterbacks, and was watched by a large audience either on television or via live stream.
